                            <i class="fas fa-times" data-c-color="stop" data-c-margin="right(.5)"></i>
                            <p data-c-margin="bottom(.25)">You’re not a current Government of Canada employee (indeterminate or term). Sorry, no exceptions</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="response-list-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-times" data-c-color="stop" data-c-margin="right(.5)"></i>
                            <p data-c-margin="bottom(.25)">You don’t have the skills needed (see below)</p>
