                        </div>
                        <div class="response-list-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-times" data-c-color="stop" data-c-margin="right(.5)"></i>
                            <p>You find it hard to adapt to new environments or processes</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
